OL,3,CWhere in the North East and North
OL,4,CYorkshire wants to become Town of
OL,5,CCulture?
OL,7,FSeveral towns across the North East
OL,8,Fand North Yorkshire have put
OL,9,Fthemselves in the race to become the
OL,10,FUK's first Town of Culture.
OL,12,FHexham, North Shields, Bishop Auckland
OL,13,Fand Whitby are among some 14 locations
OL,14,Fhoping for the crown which comes with
OL,15,Fa #3 million cash prize to deliver a
OL,16,Fprogramme of cultural events in 2028.
OL,18,FThe deadline for applications is
OL,19,FTuesday (31 March) with the winner
OL,20,Fexpected to be announced early next
OL,21,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
