OL,3,CWhere in the North East and North
OL,4,CYorkshire wants to become Town of
OL,5,CCulture?
OL,7,FWhat is 'Town of Culture'?
OL,9,FTown of Culture is a Government
OL,10,Fcompetition aimed at showcasing the
OL,11,Fcultural heritage of places around the
OL,12,FUK and the roles they have played in
OL,13,Fthe country's national story.
OL,15,FIt is based on the City of Culture
OL,16,Fscheme but aims to support smaller
OL,17,Fareas celebrating their history
OL,18,Fthrough cultural events and programmes.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
