OL,3,CWhere in the North East and North
OL,4,CYorkshire wants to become Town of
OL,5,CCulture?
OL,7,FThe winner will be given #3 million
OL,8,Ffrom the Department of Culture Media
OL,9,Fand Sport (DCMS) to deliver a cultural
OL,10,Fprogramme of events.
OL,12,FThree finalists will be chosen - a
OL,13,Fsmall, a medium and a large town -
OL,14,Fwith the two runners-up set to receive
OL,15,F#250,000.
OL,17,FWhere in the region has expressed an
OL,18,Finterest?
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
